      <title>土耳其斡旋的协议促使索马里和埃塞俄比亚关系缓和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-brokered-deal-spurs-thaw-in-somalia-ethiopia-relations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[索马里正在考虑撤销将埃塞俄比亚军队排除在打击伊斯兰叛乱分子的多国部队之外的决定，这是两国外交紧张局势缓和的另一个迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-brokered-deal-spurs-thaw-in-somalia-ethiopia-relations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 07:14:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政府称央行行长任命不会耗时太久</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/thai-government-says-bot-chair-appointment-won-t-take-too-long</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国政府希望一个遴选委员会能迅速完成选拔程序，选出新一任泰国央行行长。此前，该行的提名人因与执政党的关系而被认为不适合担任这一职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/thai-government-says-bot-chair-appointment-won-t-take-too-long</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 04:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称美国正在调查新奥尔良袭击事件和 Cyber​​truck 爆炸事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/biden-says-us-probing-new-orleans-attack-cybertruck-explosion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登表示，执法官员正在寻找其他可能参与新奥尔良袭击事件的人员，该袭击事件造成至少 15 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/biden-says-us-probing-new-orleans-attack-cybertruck-explosion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 00:47:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥推迟征收邮轮税，免除小麦关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/mexico-delays-cruise-ship-tax-exempts-wheat-from-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥推迟六个月对其港口的游轮乘客征税，同时免除 2025 年全年的小麦和化肥关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/mexico-delays-cruise-ship-tax-exempts-wheat-from-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 23:47:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普拉斯维加斯酒店附近 Cyber​​truck 爆炸事件被调查涉嫌恐怖主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/musk-says-cybertruck-explosion-near-vegas-hotel-likely-terrorism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局正在调查周三在拉斯维加斯特朗普酒店外发生的特斯拉 Cyber​​truck 爆炸事件，是否为恐怖行为，包括是否与新奥尔良发生的造成至少 15 人死亡的卡车爆炸事件有关。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/musk-says-cybertruck-explosion-near-vegas-hotel-likely-terrorism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 23:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列前国防部长加兰特表示将离开议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/ex-israel-defense-chief-gallant-says-he-s-leaving-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列前国防部长约阿夫·加兰特周三宣布，他将很快辞去议员职务，此举可能会让总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡在一些关键投票中更容易获得多数支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/ex-israel-defense-chief-gallant-says-he-s-leaving-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>檀香山烟花爆炸致 3 人死亡，20 多人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-01/a-fireworks-explosion-in-the-honolulu-area-has-killed-2-people-and-injured-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[紧急救援队抵达檀香山社区时，现场一片混乱和可怕。此前，一束大型新年烟花在点燃后翻倒，并引发剧烈爆炸，弹片飞溅，造成三人死亡，二十多人受伤，其中数人伤势严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-01/a-fireworks-explosion-in-the-honolulu-area-has-killed-2-people-and-injured-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 16:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比穆巴达拉以 290 亿美元交易额位居沙特 PIF 榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/abu-dhabi-s-mubadala-eclipses-saudi-pif-with-29-billion-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比的穆巴达拉投资公司是去年全球最活跃的主权财富基金，其加大了从私人信贷到人工智能等各个领域的交易力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/abu-dhabi-s-mubadala-eclipses-saudi-pif-with-29-billion-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 14:16:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新奥尔良袭击、 Cyber​​truck 爆炸引发美国安全担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/10-people-killed-after-vehicle-drives-into-crowd-in-new-orleans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普宣誓就任总统前不到一个月的时间里，新奥尔良发生的针对庆祝新年的狂欢者的残酷袭击使美国国内安全再次成为人们关注的焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/10-people-killed-after-vehicle-drives-into-crowd-in-new-orleans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 13:01:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰警方遭遇罕见致命袭击，司机杀死巡逻警员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-01/driver-runs-down-two-new-zealand-police-officers-killing-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠灵顿，新西兰（美联社）——该国警察局长称，元旦凌晨两名新西兰警察在徒步巡逻时被一名司机撞倒，造成一人死亡，另一人重伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-01/driver-runs-down-two-new-zealand-police-officers-killing-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 03:30:46 GMT</pubDate>
